rComments: Easy A. Teacher personality very poor.
Horrible Teaching Assistant. One of the worst classes I've taken at U of I.
Joel is really laid back. Attendance is mandatory because there are pop quizzes and in-class writings. It was pretty easy.

He's a great teacher, and has a pretty good sense of humor. You don't have to show up to class, but he does do pop quizzes. If you don't do the small readings and study the pp you won't do well. His tests are completely based on his pp, word for word. Easy A.
